to make potions listed on the cauldron cards. When everyone's five role cards have been played and actions taken, another five cards are chosen for the next set and the process repeats as before.<\/p>\n\n<p><a class=\"\" href=\"\/wiki\/page\/Games_by_player_age#\">Ages 9 and up<\/a>, a 2 on the Alea scale.<\/p>\n\n<p><a  href=\"\/boardgameexpansion\/165354\/witchs-brew-6th-player-amulets-magical-abilities\"   >Witch's Brew: The 6th Player & The Amulets & The Magical Abilities<\/a>, contained in the <a  href=\"\/boardgameexpansion\/40688\/treasure-chest\"   >Treasure Chest<\/a>, adds 3 expansions: The 1st expansion adds cards for a 6th player, as well as raven tokens to signal the game's end. The 2nd expansion adds amulets to increase the excitement in 3-player games. The 3rd expansion adds 17 magical ability cards to make certain roles particularly attractive.<\/p>\n\n","wiki":"<p><strong> <a class=\"\" href=\"\/wiki\/page\/Awards#\">Awards<\/a> <\/strong><\/p>\n\n<ul>\n    <li>2008 <a class=\"\" href=\"\/wiki\/page\/Japan_Boardgame_Prize#\">Japan Boardgame Prize<\/a>, Winner<\/li>\n    <li>2008 <a class=\"\" href=\"\/wiki\/page\/Deutscher_Spiele_Preis#\">Deutscher Spiele Preis<\/a> 9th Place.<\/li>\n    <li>2008 <a class=\"\" href=\"\/wiki\/page\/Spiel_des_Jahres#\">Spiel des Jahres<\/a> Nominee.<\/li>\n    <li>2008 <a class=\"\" href=\"\/wiki\/page\/Spiel_der_spiele#\">Spiel der spiele<\/a> (Austria), Spiele Hit mit Freunden<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<p><strong>  Contents  <\/strong><br \/>\n99 Cards:<br \/>\n   *60 Role Cards (12 per player)<br \/>\n   *31 Potion Cards (3 each of 7 Cauldrons, 2 each of 5 Shelves)<br \/>\n   *8 Spell 'Books'<\/p>\n\n<p>60 Ingredients<br \/>\n *(20 in each of the 3 colors: red, green, white)<\/p>\n\n<p>45 'potion vials'<br \/>\n24 'gold nuggets<\/p>\n\n","website":{"url":false},"imageid":"365958","images":{"thumb":"https:\/\/cf.geekdo-images.com\/thumb\/img\/Wb1WSdNIwYk0zLg-iIZubewnZIE=\/fit-in\/200x150\/pic365958.jpg","micro":"https:\/\/cf